release.body:
## What's Changed
* Feature/amp v3 by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/20
* Update year in license by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/21
* 3.0 API integrated with AC by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/22
* Add explicit queueing of fire-and-forget events by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/23
* Upgrade AC to v2 by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/24
* Task/prepare for release by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/25
* Update to AC v2.0.0-beta2 by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/26
* Update annotated-container, amp, psalm by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/27
* Update Annotated Container, add ThirdPartyInitializer by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/28
* Update AC 2.0.0-rc3, use correct initializer by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/29
* Remove annotated container autowiring, rename EventListener by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/30
* Add ListenerProvider, completely move annotated container to separate… by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/31
* Thoroughly remove remaining references to Annotated Container by @cspray in https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/pull/32


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/labrador-kennel/async-event/compare/2.3.0...3.0.0

release.body:
## What's Changed
* Feature/constraint protected delegated#312 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/324
* Add check for a service with duplicate names. Fix #311 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/325
* Task/improve abstract container factory by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/327
* Add command to run logical constraint checks by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/332
* Feature/non public service prepare/313 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/335
* Add check for duplicate service types by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/336
* Allow creating a delegated parameter store factory by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/337
* Feature/constraint multiple service prepare by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/338
* Feature/illuminate container v2 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/339
* Feature/constraint multiple service delegate by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/340
* Task/update for 2 2 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/341


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/compare/v2.1.0...v2.2.0
